  "text": "Cady et al. [CITATION_1] present various e-Learning environments used by middle school math and science teachers. For the mathematical courses, they use Blackboard for asynchronous activities and Centra for the synchronous activities, providing voice interactions with participants. Other tools were Geometer's Sketchpad and Notetaker. For the science courses, they used Blackboard and WordPress.",
